text: Munchos are a potato chips snack food. They are manufactured from dehydrated potatoes by Frito-Lay. They are somewhat similar to Lay's Stax and Pringles. These are also made with dried potatoes. They are kosher. The chips were first made in 1969. ==References== Category:1969 establishments in the United States Category:Snack foods
title: Munchos
